data.description: Rare find, PRIME location just walking distance from the downtown Crown Point square, the fairgrounds, schools, shopping, and all the good pubs and eatery. Also situated on nearly a full acre!!! Walking in you'll notice the original flooring, but updated colors, kitchen, sun(or play room) and main floor ensuite. Upstairs offers 2 additional generous size rooms and bathroom. Downstairs offering an additional living, office, and plenty of storage! Walking onto the large back deck you'll notice ample room for multiple patio sets and entertainment space, the pool, and the yard that goes on for many outdoor gatherings!
